params.sqlcmd: "SELECT " +" A.APPR_ID, " +" A.SCREEN_URL, " +" A.STATUS, " +" A.PROC_TYP, " +" A.REQUEST_BY, " +" B.USER_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(A.REQUEST_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.APPR_REMARKS, " +" A.RESERVE_CAUSE, " +" A.MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" USER_MST B, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D " +"WHERE " +" A.REQUEST_BY = ? " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = B.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +"ORDER BY A.APPR_ID"

"SELECT " +" A.APPR_ID, " +" A.SCREEN_URL, " +" A.STATUS, " +" A.PROC_TYP, " +" A.REQUEST_BY, " +" E.USER_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(A.REQUEST_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.APPR_REMARKS, " +" A.RESERVE_CAUSE, " +" A.MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D, " +" USER_MST E, " +" USER_MST F, " +" T_TRAN_SRC G " +"WHERE " +" A.STATUS = '1' " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = E.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +" AND F.USER_CD = ? " +" AND G.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(G.FIELD_NAME = 'l_OWN_ORG_CD' " +" OR G.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD') " +" AND G.FIELD_VALUE = F.SECTION_CD " +"ORDER BY " +" A.APPR_ID"

"SELECT " +" A.APPR_ID, " +" A.SCREEN_URL, " +" A.STATUS, " +" A.PROC_TYP, " +" A.REQUEST_BY, " +" E.USER_NAME, " +" TO_CHAR(A.REQUEST_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.APPR_REMARKS, " +" A.RESERVE_CAUSE, " +" A.MODIFY_COUNT " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D, " +" USER_MST E, " +" USER_MST F, " +" T_TRAN_SRC G " +"WHERE " +" A.STATUS = '2' " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = E.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +" AND F.USER_CD = ? " +" AND G.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(G.FIELD_NAME = 'l_OWN_ORG_CD' " +" OR G.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD') " +" AND G.FIELD_VALUE = F.SECTION_CD " +"ORDER BY " +" A.APPR_ID"
"SELECT " +" A.FIELD_NAME, " +" A.FIELD_VALUE, " +" A.FIELD_FLG " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_SRC A " +"WHERE " +" A.APPR_ID = ?"

"SELECT " +" A.ODR_NO, " +" A.ODR_TYP, " +" A.CUST_ODR_NO, " +" B.CUST_CD, " +" B.CUST_ITEM_CD, " +" A.DLV_LOC_CD, " +" A.ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(A.DESINATED_DLV_DATE,'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" A.SPCL_PRICE_TYP, " +" A.ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" A.REMARKS " +"FROM " +" T_ODR A, " +" T_ODR_CTL B " +"WHERE " +" A.ODR_NO = ? " +" AND A.ODR_CTL_NO = B.ODR_CTL_NO"
"SELECT " +" A.APPR_ID " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A " +"WHERE " +" A.APPR_ID = ? " +" AND A.MODIFY_COUNT = ?"

"SELECT " +" COUNT(1) " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" USER_MST B, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D " +"WHERE " +" A.REQUEST_BY = ? " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = B.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +" AND ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"SELECT " +" COUNT(1) " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D, " +" USER_MST E, " +" USER_MST F, " +" T_TRAN_SRC G " +"WHERE " +" A.STATUS = '1' " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = E.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +" AND F.USER_CD = ? " +" AND G.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(G.FIELD_NAME = 'l_OWN_ORG_CD' " +" OR G.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD') " +" AND G.FIELD_VALUE = F.SECTION_CD " +" AND ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"SELECT " +" COUNT(1) " +"FROM " +" T_TRAN_APR A, " +" T_TRAN_SRC C, " +" T_TRAN_SRC D, " +" USER_MST E, " +" USER_MST F, " +" T_TRAN_SRC G " +"WHERE " +" A.STATUS = '2' " +" AND A.REQUEST_BY = E.USER_CD " +" AND C.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(C.FIELD_NAME = 'l_ODR_ACPT_DATE' " +" OR C.FIELD_NAME = 'ODR_ACPT_DATE') " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE >= ? " +" AND C.FIELD_VALUE <= ? " +" AND D.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(D.FIELD_NAME = 'l_CUST_CD' " +" OR D.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CD') " +" AND D.FIELD_VALUE LIKE ? " +" AND F.USER_CD = ? " +" AND G.APPR_ID = A.APPR_ID " +" AND(G.FIELD_NAME = 'l_OWN_ORG_CD' " +" OR G.FIELD_NAME = 'CUST_CHRG_ORG_CD') " +" AND G.FIELD_VALUE = F.SECTION_CD " +" AND ROWNUM <= TO_NUMBER(?) + 1"

"SELECT " +" ODR_NO, " +" '3' ODR_TYP, " +" CUST_ODR_NO, " +" CUST_CD, " +" '' CUST_ITEM_CD, " +" '' DLV_LOC_CD, " +" ODR_QTY, " +" TO_CHAR(DESINATED_DLV_DATE, 'YYYY/MM/DD'), " +" '1' SPCL_PRICE_TYP, " +" ODR_UNIT_PRICE, " +" REMARKS " +"FROM " +" T_ODR_UNSTOCK " +"WHERE " +" ODR_NO = ?"
